===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# (Shakespearian) A woman who is "no longer fresh" or who has lost her virginity, as in Shakespeare's ''Much Ado About Nothing''
#: ''"I stand dishonor'd, that have gone about/To link my dear friend to a common stale" (Act IV, Scene i, lines 59-60)''

